HEADWORD: Brownstone
<hw>Brown"stone`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
dark variety of sandstone, much used for building purposes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a building, especially a dwelling, faced with
